Furniture, Home Decor, Interior Design&Decorating Ideas Search for: Home » Restaurant » Wienerwald Fast Food: Eco Friendly Restaurant Interior Design February 22, 2011 Wienerwald Fast Food: Eco Friendly Restaurant Interior Design Category: Restaurant s p o n s o r e d l i n k s
This comfortable Wienerwald restaurant interior was completes this hang-out space. Actually, this place was not only can use as the common space for eat but also as a space for gathering with our family or friends. Today, the function of a food space was change. We will see the young generation love to spend their leisure time in restaurant space just for relax and enjoy their free time. There were also several officer or employee who use this place as the place for getting deal for their business. Through see those functions, these inspiring restaurant design plans were completed with the contemporary dining room and relaxed space for getting a conversation. The furniture plans have to combine with the interior plans so that thematic look will be perfect. This eco-friendly Wienerwald fast food chicken design was come from the color paint of the wall space (interior) and the supporting application of plants. Those natural restaurant inspirations can be seen in this green and clean bar lounge restaurant. [ Ippolito Fleitz ]
